<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | Discord 인증 시스템</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="flex items-start justify-center min-h-screen pt-10 pb-10">
    <div class="main-container p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-3xl text-left transform">
        <header class="mb-6 border-b pb-4">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold nav-link-active"><%= title %></h1>
            <nav class="mt-2 text-sm">
                <a href="/" class="<%= title.includes('환영합니다') ? 'nav-link-active' : 'nav-link-normal' %> hover:underline font-medium mr-4">시스템 소개</a>
                <a href="/QnA" class="<%= title.includes('Q&A') ? 'nav-link-active' : 'nav-link-normal' %> hover:underline">자주 묻는 질문</a>
                <a href="/invite" class="text-green-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline font-medium ml-4">봇 초대</a>
                <a href="/dashboard/login" class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline ml-4">관리자 대시보드</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <div class="markdown-content"><%- contentHtml %></div>
        <footer class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t text-sm text-center footer-text">이 페이지는 디스코드 서버 인증 시스템의 일부입니다.</footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
